{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e2f731ce83","title":"“肃反是违反宪法的行为”","origin":"《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"93add9207d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"e2f731ce83"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"c8c474caaa","name":"天津大学"},{"id":"f82eea7b12","name":"包诚"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"441174d7a6","type":"title","text":"“肃反是违反宪法的行为”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e2f731ce83"},{"id":"0ed7cfba8d","type":"authors","text":"天津大学包诚","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e2f731ce83"},{"id":"027b34a87d","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反的错误是党的政策的错误，党的主张宁“左”勿右，肃反时同学们是昧着良心去怀疑别人，这种大胆怀疑政策对人进行斗争是违反宪法的行为。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e2f731ce83"},{"id":"3d0e290e3d","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反没有法律也没有政府，一切全是党的系统，全是党员了，在没有什么事情的时候，才把政府搬出来。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e2f731ce83"},{"id":"74cbb2d7ea","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反的目的是达到了，但错误是大大的，肃反的错误，造成党和群众的隔阂，党中央对肃反的百分数的估计是不科学的。党员相信党中央，就好像教徒信耶稣一般。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e2f731ce83"}],"page":{"id":"ff6c9c1167","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e2f731ce83","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}